We need to think of something more.

03:15.541 --> 03:16.625
I've got it.

03:16.750 --> 03:18.250
I do believe...

03:18.375 --> 03:20.666
I think I just...

03:20.791 --> 03:23.166
If we take that part, and, uh...

03:23.291 --> 03:25.708
Awesome.

03:43.791 --> 03:45.833
It's a Crick-O-Wheel.

03:45.916 --> 03:49.833
