05:19.125 --> 05:21.208
Whoa.

05:25.125 --> 05:27.500
The Faraway Golden Tree.

05:32.291 --> 05:35.875
You know the old saying,
"Whoever snuffed it, fluffed it."

05:36.000 --> 05:37.708
Well, that was my dad.

05:42.708 --> 05:44.708
Oh, my goodness gracious.

05:44.833 --> 05:46.166
Are you okay?

05:46.625 --> 05:49.250
