06:55.375 --> 06:57.208
Oh, no.

07:00.125 --> 07:01.458
That's it.

07:18.458 --> 07:21.041
You know if there are height restrictions?

07:21.125 --> 07:24.875
Oh, dear. I'm a little overexcited.

07:25.000 --> 07:26.791
